* Included missing 20.1.2 content.


Version 21.0.0 (2010-04-23)
===========================

* Toolchain 2.0.1 for st40.


Version 20.1.2 (2010-04-22)
===========================

* Cleaned SPLIT_TARGETS stuff.
* Made cleaning a bit more verbose.


Version 20.1.1 (2010-04-14)
